Given	I'm logged-in with valid credentials
And	I'm on Page 04 of Feet MRI
And I select 'Finding' radio button

When I select 'Fracture' from the dropdown menu
Then 'Add new finding' button is enabled
And a single selection localizer is enabled

When I click on the localizer
And I select 'Distal Tibia'
And I close the localizer
Then '43A' radio button is enabled
And '43B' radio button is enabled
And '43C' radio button is enabled
And '43: Not further specified' radio button is enabled

When I select '43A' radio button
Then '43A1' radio button is enabled
And '43A2' radio button is enabled
And '43A3' radio button is enabled

When I select '43A1' radio button
Then '43A1.1' radio button is enabled
And '43A1.2' radio button is enabled
And '43A1.3' radio button is enabled

When I select '43A2' radio button
Then '43A2.1' radio button is enabled
And '43A2.2' radio button is enabled
And '43A2.3' radio button is enabled

When I select '43A3' radio button
Then '43A3.1' radio button is enabled
And '43A3.2' radio button is enabled
And '43A3.3' radio button is enabled


When I select '43B' radio button
Then '43B1' radio button is enabled
And '43B2' radio button is enabled
And '43B3' radio button is enabled

When I select '43B1' radio button
Then '43B1.1' radio button is enabled
And '43B1.2' radio button is enabled
And '43B1.3' radio button is enabled

When I select '43B1.1' radio button
Then 'o: Anterior' checkbox is enabled
And 'y: Posterior, Volkmann' checkbox is enabled

When I select '43B1.2' radio button
Then 'f: Lateral' checkbox is enabled
And 'z: Med. articular surface incl. med. malleolus' checkbox is enabled

When I select '43B2' radio button
Then '43B2.1' radio button is enabled
And '43B2.2' radio button is enabled
And '43B2.3' radio button is enabled

When I select '43B2.1' radio button
Then 'o: Anterior' checkbox is enabled
And 'y: Posterior, Volkmann' checkbox is enabled

When I select '43B2.2' radio button
Then 'f: Lateral' checkbox is enabled
And 'h: Medial' checkbox is enabled

When I select '43B3' radio button
Then '43B3.1' radio button is enabled
And '43B3.2' radio button is enabled
And '43B3.3' radio button is enabled

When I select '43B3.1' radio button
Then 'o: Anterior' checkbox is enabled
And 'y: Posterior, Volkmann' checkbox is enabled

When I select '43B3.2' radio button
Then 'f: Lateral' checkbox is enabled
And 'h: Medial' checkbox is enabled


When I select '43C' radio button
Then '43C1' radio button is enabled
And '43C2' radio button is enabled
And '43C3' radio button is enabled

When I select '43C1' radio button
Then '43C1.1' radio button is enabled
And '43C1.2' radio button is enabled
And '43C1.3' radio button is enabled

When I select '43C1.1' radio button
Then 'q: Frontal/coronal plane' checkbox is enabled
And 'r: Sagittal plane' checkbox is enabled

When I select '43C2' radio button
Then '43C2.1' radio button is enabled
And '43C2.2' radio button is enabled
And '43C1.3' radio button is enabled

When I select '43C2.1' radio button
Then 'q: Frontal/coronal plane' checkbox is enabled
And 'r: Sagittal plane' checkbox is enabled

When I select '43C3' radio button
Then '43C3.1' radio button is enabled
And '43C3.2' radio button is enabled
And '43C3.3' radio button is enabled


When I select '43: Not further specified'
Then 'Consolidated fracture' radio button is enabled
And 'Suspicion of' radio button is enabled
